Some needed craftable supplies are wanted by the Zhélruka settlers.

Craft worthy items and exchange them for Embers of Enchantment at a Mote and Ember Trader in Bree, Galtrev, the Twenty-first Hall, or Mózhek near the Stable-master in Skarháld.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest can be turned in once per week.</rgb>
DNT 'oh thank you for the items they will be a big help'
DNT please craft me some things
'Why look at this craft-work. These will serve us well, take my word.'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>The quantity of Ember-worthy Crafts will be removed from your inventory.</rgb>
